1. *Razumeš* li da ti je potrebno da se obrazuješ? (Do you understand that you need to get educated?) 
2. *Razumeš* li me? (Do you understand me?)
3. Da li *razumeš*? (Do you understand?)
4. *Razumem* šta govoriš. (I understand what you are saying.)
5. *Razume* li on to? (Does he understand it?)
6. Mislim da *razume*š. (I think you understand.)